{"ja411:0.1":"Jataka ","ja411:0.2":"Sattakanipata ","ja411:0.3":"Gandharavagga ","ja411:0.4":"6. Susimajataka ","ja411:1.1":"“Kalani kesani pure ahesum, ","ja411:1.2":"Jatani sisamhi yathapadese; ","ja411:1.3":"Tanajja setani susima disva, ","ja411:1.4":"Dhammam cara brahmacariyassa kalo”. ","ja411:2.1":"“Mameva deva palitam na tuyham, ","ja411:2.2":"Mameva sisam mama uttamangam; ","ja411:2.3":"‘Attham karissan’ti musa abhanim, ","ja411:2.4":"Ekaparadham khama rajasettha. ","ja411:3.1":"Daharo tuvam dassaniyosi raja, ","ja411:3.2":"Pathamuggato hosi yatha kaliro; ","ja411:3.3":"Rajjanca karehi mamanca passa, ","ja411:3.4":"Ma kalikam anudhavi janinda”. ","ja411:4.1":"“Passami voham daharim kumarim, ","ja411:4.2":"Samatthapassam sutanum sumajjham; ","ja411:4.3":"Kalappavalava pavellamana, ","ja411:4.4":"Palobhayantiva naresu gacchati. ","ja411:5.1":"Tamena passamiparena narim, ","ja411:5.2":"Asitikam navutikam va jacca; ","ja411:5.3":"Dandam gahetvana pavedhamanam, ","ja411:5.4":"Gopanasibhoggasamam carantim. ","ja411:6.1":"Soham tamevanuvicintayanto, ","ja411:6.2":"Eko sayami sayanassa majjhe; ","ja411:6.3":"‘Ahampi evam’ iti pekkhamano, ","ja411:6.4":"Na gahe rame brahmacariyassa kalo. ","ja411:7.1":"Rajjuvalambani cesa, ","ja411:7.2":"Ya gehe vasato rati; ","ja411:7.3":"Evampi chetvana vajanti dhira, ","ja411:7.4":"Anapekkhino kamasukham pahaya”ti. ","ja411:8.1":"Susimajatakam chattham. "}